---
import Hero from "../Components/hero.astro";
import Layout from "../Layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About: Earth Charity">
    <Hero>
        <Fragment slot="title"> About Earth Charity </Fragment>
        <Fragment slot="description"
            >We are a charity that helps the environment.</Fragment
        >
    </Hero>

    <section>
        <p>
            At Earth Charity, we believe in creating a sustainable future for
            all life on our planet. Founded in 2020, our organization works
            tirelessly to combat climate change, protect endangered species, and
            preserve vital ecosystems across the globe.
        </p>
        <p>
            Through partnerships with local communities, scientists, and
            environmental experts, we implement practical solutions to pressing
            environmental challenges. From reforestation projects in the Amazon
            to marine conservation initiatives in the Pacific, our work spans
            continents and ecosystems.
        </p>
        <p>
            What sets us apart is our commitment to transparency and measurable
            impact. Every dollar donated goes directly to carefully selected
            projects, with regular updates provided to our supporters.
        </p>
        <p>
            Join us in our mission to protect and restore Earth's natural beauty
            for generations to come.
        </p>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    section {
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
</style>
